Pronunciation[edit]

  • (Classical) IPA(key): /proːˈkur.roː/, [proːˈkʊr.roː]
  • (Ecclesiastical) IPA(key): /proˈkur.ro/, [prɔˈkur.rɔ]

Verb[edit]

prōcurrō (present infinitive prōcurrere, perfect active prōcucurrī or prōcurrī, supine prōcursum); third conjugation

  1. I run or rush forwards
  2. I advance
  3. I jut out
